mil.emp3.api.events

Class MapStateChangeEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.emp3.api.events.Event<MapEventEnum,IMap>
      • mil.emp3.api.events.MapStateChangeEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEvent<MapEventEnum,IMap>

    public abstract class MapStateChangeEvent
extends Event<MapEventEnum,IMap>
    This event is generated when a specific map changes state. To register for this event you must instantiate an object that implements the IMapStateChangeEventListener interface and register for the event on an IMap.
